# Orchestration Rules

## Memory Bank Rules
* Read memory bank files at task start
* Memory bank should contain:
<name_of_feature>_plan.md
<name_of_feature>_descissions.md
* Initialize if not exist (create folder /memorybank)

## Task Assignment Rules

### Plan Mode Tasks
* Requirements analysis
* Architecture decisions
* Design patterns
* Technical specifications

### Actmode Tasks
* Implementation work
* Testing and validation
* Documentation updates

## Monitoring Rules
* Track attempt_completion signals
* Validate outcomes against requirements
* Create 'actmode' tasks only after 'plan' completion
* Update Memory Bank with progress
* Maintain task dependency graph

## Completion Requirements
* Verify all subtasks completed
* Validate integration points
* Update Memory Bank
* Synthesize final results 